Node.RefEnglish: {Israel priests Levites temple servants descendants of}

Node.Notes: Tree assumes: some from the sons of Judah and some from the sons of Benjamin lived in Jerusalem.
Uncertain. Tree assumes Shabbethai and Jozabad [were] oer the work ... from among the heads of the Levites.
Uncertain. Assumes: a command of the king [was] upon them and a firm ordinance [was] upon the singers concerning the matter of day in its day (i.e., the matter of each day).
